  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979410/extras/3539771f4a7a25b2fd83676b6a1fbe3c.poster.avif?t=1738350095\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979410/extras/3539771f4a7a25b2fd83676b6a1fbe3c.webm?t=1738350095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979410/extras/3539771f4a7a25b2fd83676b6a1fbe3c.mp4?t=1738350095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ROGUELIKE AIR COMBAT - ARCADE ACTION</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short, intense and randomized runs: typical sessions are 10-20 min long</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tech-up and upgrade your strafe-capable supersonic VTOL mid-flight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Score-attack on the daily leaderboards: reset every 36 hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 difficulty levels (operations): featuring different length, intensity and score potential</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimum requirements: quick installation and runs on 10+ years old hardware</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979410/extras/1496e34b4d836d89b064adcd3c73d722.poster.avif?t=1738350095\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979410/extras/1496e34b4d836d89b064adcd3c73d722.webm?t=1738350095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979410/extras/1496e34b4d836d89b064adcd3c73d722.mp4?t=1738350095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EASY TO PICKUP - HARD TO MASTER</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One fire button: hold for guns, tap for missiles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One target button: hold for cinematic zoom and aim-assist</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One thrust button + strafe to dodge enemy fire</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FPS-like control scheme for mouse & keyboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xbox controller support - <i>Others & HOTAS supported with Steam Input</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979410/extras/9605dc7f3298cd1107094c5c5342b9ce.poster.avif?t=1738350095\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979410/extras/9605dc7f3298cd1107094c5c5342b9ce.webm?t=1738350095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979410/extras/9605dc7f3298cd1107094c5c5342b9ce.mp4?t=1738350095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
